{"tid":1516750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"想3分鐘知道香港係咪就玩完？睇「港聞精讀」第三期啦！","createTime":"2019-08-29T16:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:06:56.000Z","uid":89974,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc56068881c74caee1e4083ab9c65c5341534b9","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"想3分鐘內一次過睇哂所有大單野？<br />\n想俾你既港豬朋友知而家香港有幾大獲？<br />\n想潛移默化你既淺藍父母？<br />\n想搵野貼下連儂牆？<br />\n想airdrop俾陌生人又唔想俾佢reject你？<br />\n想知有咩文宣可以打？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港聞精讀幫到你！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NZoWz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NZoWz5.jpg&h=c204d5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢份精讀包含8月27至8月29號既所有重大新聞，由淺藍到深黃都值得睇<br />\n幫大家refresh下發生咩事，打文宣同國際戰線只要照住份野嚟打就無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<br />\nQ1.梁國雄議員，字細到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA1.輕輕一按放大張圖就會見到啲字好清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ2.你地幾時會出一篇新？<br />\nA2.預計就每2日有一篇新刊，但係要視乎工作量同有幾多大單野<br />\n<br />\nQ3.呢啲料我夠知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA3.仲有好多人唔知嫁！<span style=\"color: red;\">Airdrop</span>傳出去俾班中產中立撚叫佢地企埋同一陣線，貼埋連儂牆就更加好啦<br />\n<br />\nQ4.有無英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA4.英文版會視乎今次反應如何再搵人手翻譯，到時我要見到twitter全部都係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ5.咪有牆紙整緊囉<br />\nA5.牆紙係深入既報章，我地呢份俾無乜時間既人睇，食個早餐搭下黨鐵，只需要3分鐘就知道哂香港就嚟玩完，成件事係幾咁寫意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以記得<span style=\"color: red;\">Airdrop</span>出去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5159aaec3513b5ade452fd10f3070afbc438bdf8","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"3ef28f6e9ffc80b3503e7f3eee18d5ee60ccff6f","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7ac057806f675a55dcfdc1250c932a73f95c0c0b","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca78ccc68bc83e0e828f1e77f49840bfece990d","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8e275c1b497014a18bcac644d7b0ebc18964af","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd61e7ce8361407993fbcd244b521937dc0e9686","tid":1516750,"uid":232417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a3da422b7193aadc4b193741a411c63aac74e81","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b81652d4d99793e162be341fb4195a5da1f587e","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cbfc3cc31ec79d8b8905b30cc73f512a9aa210","tid":1516750,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3550d4509e02a7fef162545ad5a60eed8226036e","tid":1516750,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/